{"name": "polimer", "metadata": {"name": "polimer", "version": "0.0.2", "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3"], "home_page": null, "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": [], "summary": "Automated callstack synthesis framework (annotations-based)", "upload_time": 1735565480}, "documentation": ["# polimer\n\n**polimer** is an automated callstack synthesis framework (based on annotations)\n\n## Basic idea\n\n- Define annotations based on payload id (not just type id)\n    - e.g. `l: 'price_list'` insead of `l: list`\n- Automatically invoke argument initializers based on payload id\n    - e.g. call `def get_price_list() -> 'price_list'`\n- Simplify end-user code\n\n## Quick-demo\n\n1. Install **polimer**\n```bash\npip install polimer\n```\n\n2. Annotate your methods with payload ids:\n\n<h5 a><strong><code>prices.py</code></strong></h5>\n\n```python\nimport random\n\ndef get_prices(length=10) -> 'price_list':\n    return [random.random() for _ in range(length)]\n\ndef calc_avg_price(p: 'price_list'):\n    return sum(p) / len(p)\n```\n\n3. Import your entrypoints via **polimer**\n<h5 a><strong><code>demo.py</code></strong></h5>\n\n```python\nfrom prices import *\nfrom polimer import prices\n\nprint(prices.calc_avg_price())\n```\n"], "modules": [{"name": "polimer", "documentation": ["Copyright, Aleksey Boev 2024"], "functions": [{"name": "polimer.load_functions", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "polimer.build_dep_tree", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "functions", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "polimer.topology_sort", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "dep_tree", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "start_f_id", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "polimer.prepare_kwargs", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "function", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "artifacts", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "kwargs", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "polimer.run_chain", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "chain", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "functions", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "kwargs", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "polimer.run", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "f_id", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "user_kwargs", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "polimer.get_func", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "f_id", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [{"name": "polimer.functions", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "polimer.deepcopy", "xref": {"fqname": "copy.deepcopy", "project": null}}, {"name": "polimer.deque", "xref": {"fqname": "collections.deque", "project": null}}, {"name": "polimer.ModuleType", "xref": {"fqname": "types.ModuleType", "project": null}}]}]}